<aside class="ss-promo reveal" aria-label="Sponsored — Shadow Software LLC">
  <div class="ss-promo-inner">
    <div class="ss-promo-brand">
      <img src="/logos/shadow-software.webp" alt="Shadow Software LLC" class="ss-promo-logo" width="32" height="32">
      <span class="ss-promo-sponsor">Shadow Software LLC</span>
    </div>
    <p class="ss-promo-eyebrow">You found this article through search — that's not an accident.</p>
    <p class="ss-promo-heading">We build <em>search visibility</em> for serious brands.</p>
    <p class="ss-promo-body">SEO &amp; AEO services that get your business in front of people the moment they're asking the right questions — in Google, and in AI.</p>
    <div class="ss-promo-pills">
      <span class="ss-promo-pill">Technical SEO</span>
      <span class="ss-promo-pill">Answer Engine Optimization</span>
      <span class="ss-promo-pill">Content Strategy</span>
      <span class="ss-promo-pill">AI Search Visibility</span>
    </div>
    <div class="ss-promo-cta-wrap">
      <a href="https://shadowsoftware.com/services/seo" class="ss-promo-cta" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer sponsored">
        Get found like this
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <line x1="2" y1="7" x2="12" y2="7"/>
          <polyline points="8 3 12 7 8 11"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</aside>

<style>
  .ss-promo {
    margin: 3rem 0 2rem;
    border-radius: 5px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #0f0f0f;
    border: 1px solid rgba(143, 212, 104, 0.2);
    box-shadow:
      0 0 0 1px rgba(143, 212, 104, 0.04),
      0 4px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4),
      0 0 60px rgba(143, 212, 104, 0.05);
  }

  .ss-promo-inner {
    padding: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .ss-promo-inner::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -60px;
    right: -60px;
    width: 240px;
    height: 240px;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(143, 212, 104, 0.14) 0%, transparent 68%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .ss-promo-brand {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.625rem;
  }

  .ss-promo-logo {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    object-fit: contain;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .ss-promo-sponsor {
    font-size: 0.625rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(143, 212, 104, 0.65);
  }

  .ss-promo-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.42) !important;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0 !important;
  }

  .ss-promo-heading {
    font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 4vw, 1.875rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    color: #fff !important;
    margin: 0 !important;
    text-transform: none !important;
    text-decoration: none !important;
  }

  .ss-promo-heading em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: #8FD468;
  }

  .ss-promo-body {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55) !important;
    margin: 0 !important;
    max-width: 44ch;
  }

  .ss-promo-pills {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.375rem;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .ss-promo-pill {
    font-size: 0.5625rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.09em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.625rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
    background: rgba(143, 212, 104, 0.07);
    border: 1px solid rgba(143, 212, 104, 0.18);
    color: #8FD468;
  }

  .ss-promo-cta-wrap {
    display: flex;
  }

  .ss-promo-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.7rem 1.375rem;
    background: #8FD468;
    color: #060606 !important;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    border-radius: 3px;
    text-decoration: none !important;
    transition: background 0.2s ease, transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .ss-promo-cta:hover {
    background: #a0e37e;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(143, 212, 104, 0.3);
    color: #060606 !important;
  }

  .ss-promo-cta svg {
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .ss-promo-cta:hover svg {
    transform: translateX(3px);
  }

  @media print {
    .ss-promo { display: none; }
  }
</style>
